---
import { Palette, FileText, Image, Sparkles } from 'lucide-react';
---

<section id="branding" class="w-full bg-gray-50 py-12 sm:py-16">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-10 sm:mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-black mb-4">
        <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-600 to-blue-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent">Branding y Diseño Gráfico</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Identidad visual completa que refleja la esencia de tu marca y genera conexión emocional con tu audiencia.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6 sm:gap-8">
      
      <!-- Creación de logo -->
      <div class="group p-6 sm:p-8 rounded-xl border-2 border-gray-200 hover:border-purple-600 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 cursor-pointer bg-white">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 sm:w-14 sm:h-14 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4 bg-purple-100">
          <Sparkles className="w-6 h-6 sm:w-7 sm:h-7 text-purple-600" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-black mb-2">
          Creación de Logo
        </h3>
        <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          Diseño de logo único y memorable que representa la identidad y valores de tu marca.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Identidad visual -->
      <div class="group p-6 sm:p-8 rounded-xl border-2 border-gray-200 hover:border-blue-600 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 cursor-pointer bg-white">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 sm:w-14 sm:h-14 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4 bg-blue-100">
          <Palette className="w-6 h-6 sm:w-7 sm:h-7 text-blue-600" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-black mb-2">
          Identidad Visual
        </h3>
        <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          Sistema completo de identidad visual que proyecta coherencia y profesionalismo en todos tus canales.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Manual de marca -->
      <div class="group p-6 sm:p-8 rounded-xl border-2 border-gray-200 hover:border-purple-600 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 cursor-pointer bg-white">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 sm:w-14 sm:h-14 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4 bg-purple-100">
          <FileText className="w-6 h-6 sm:w-7 sm:h-7 text-purple-600" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-black mb-2">
          Manual de Marca
        </h3>
        <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          Guía completa de uso de marca que asegura la consistencia visual en todas tus aplicaciones.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Diseño de piezas gráficas -->
      <div class="group p-6 sm:p-8 rounded-xl border-2 border-gray-200 hover:border-blue-600 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 cursor-pointer bg-white">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 sm:w-14 sm:h-14 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4 bg-blue-100">
          <Image className="w-6 h-6 sm:w-7 sm:h-7 text-blue-600" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-black mb-2">
          Piezas Gráficas
        </h3>
        <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          Diseño de flyers, contenido digital y piezas gráficas que destacan y comunican tu mensaje de forma efectiva.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

